rov:RegisteredOrganization a rdfs:Class .
rov:RegisteredOrganization skos:definition "an organization that gains legal entity status by the act of registration. Compare to org:FormalOrganization
 that applies to any legal entity, including those created by other legal means. Registered organizations are distinct from
 the broader concept of organizations, groups or, in some jurisdictions, sole traders. Many organizations exist that are
not legal entities yet to the outside world they have staff, hierarchies, locations etc. Other organizations exist that are
 an umbrella for several legal entities (universities are often good examples of this) [rov:]
A legal person or structure that is organized under the laws of any jurisdiction [lei-elf:]" .
rov:RegisteredOrganization skos:example "Examples include, without limitation [lei-elf:]: all financial intermediaries, banks and finance companies,
all entities that issue equity, debt or other 
securities for other capital structures, all entities listed on an exchange,  all entities that trade stock or debt, investment
vehicles, including mutual funds, pension funds and alternative investment vehicles constituted as corporate entities or
collective investment agreements (including umbrella funds as well as funds under an umbrella structure, hedge funds,
private equity funds, etc.), all entities under the purview of a financial regulator and their affiliates, subsidiaries and
holding companies, counterparties to financial transactions." .

ebg:DataItem a rdfs:Class .

ebg:isPubliclyTraded a rdf:Property, owl:DatatypeProperty .
ebg:isPubliclyTraded schema:domainIncludes rov:RegisteredOrganization .
ebg:isPubliclyTraded schema:rangeIncludes xsd:boolean .
ebg:isPubliclyTraded skos:definition "Whether the company is publicly traded (listed at a stock exchange) [ebg:]" .

ebg:orgStatus a rdf:Property, owl:DatatypeProperty .
ebg:orgStatus schema:domainIncludes rov:RegisteredOrganization .
ebg:orgStatus schema:rangeIncludes xsd:string .
ebg:orgStatus skos:scopeNote "There is no globally accepted list of company states.
For Inactive, some look at hard evidence (the company has been deregistered), others at a long period of
inactivity (dormant). Because of this, a user cannot assume that Active and Inactive are opposites." .
ebg:orgStatus skos:definition "Flag that identifies whether a company is active or not [ebg:]. The operational and/or legal 
registration status of the entity [lei:]" .
ebg:orgStatus skos:examples "'insolvent', 'bankrupt', 'in receivership': likely to mean slightly different things with different
legal implications in different jurisdictions [rov:] 'Normal Activity': does appear to have cross-border
usefulness and this should be used in preference to terms like 'trading' or 'operating' [rov:] 'Actively trading'
vs 'Dormant' vs 'Unregistered' could be considered the 3 main divisions of Status" .
ebg:orgStatus skos:rules "A Best Practice for recording status levels is to use the relevant jurisdiction's terms
and to encode these in a SKOS Concept Scheme. [rov:]" .

schema:foundingDate a rdf:Property, owl:DatatypeProperty .
schema:foundingDate schema:domainIncludes rov:RegisteredOrganization .
schema:foundingDate schema:rangeIncludes xsd:date .
schema:foundingDate skos:example "2010-11-18"^^xsd:date .

ebg:juristiction a rdf:Property, owl:DatatypeProperty .
ebg:juristiction schema:domainIncludes rov:RegisteredOrganization .
ebg:juristiction schema:rangeIncludes xsd:string .

ebg:newsFeed a rdf:Property, owl:DatatypeProperty .
ebg:newsFeed schema:domainIncludes rov:RegisteredOrganization .
ebg:newsFeed schema:rangeIncludes xsd:anyURI .

schema:availableLanguage a rdf:Property, owl:DatatypeProperty .
schema:availableLanguage schema:domainIncludes rov:RegisteredOrganization .
schema:availableLanguage schema:rangeIncludes xsd:string .
schema:availableLanguage skos:definition "Languages used by the organization" .
schema:availableLanguage skos:scopeNote "Deduced from languages appearing in web resources related to the organisation" .
schema:availableLanguage skos:example "it" .

schema:dissolutionDate a rdf:Property, owl:DatatypeProperty .
schema:dissolutionDate schema:domainIncludes rov:RegisteredOrganization .
schema:dissolutionDate schema:rangeIncludes xsd:date .
schema:dissolutionDate skos:definition "Date when the organization was dissolved or removed from register" .
schema:dissolutionDate skos:example "2010-11"^^xsd:gYearMonth .

ebg:about a rdf:Property, owl:ObjectProperty .
ebg:about schema:domainIncludes rov:RegisteredOrganization .
ebg:about schema:rangeIncludes ebg:DataItem .

ebg:providedCompanyData a rdf:Property, owl:ObjectProperty .
ebg:providedCompanyData schema:domainIncludes rov:RegisteredOrganization .
ebg:providedCompanyData schema:rangeIncludes ebg:DataItem .

rov:orgStatus a rdf:Property, owl:DatatypeProperty .
rov:orgStatus schema:domainIncludes rov:RegisteredOrganization .
rov:orgStatus schema:rangeIncludes skos:Concept .
rov:orgStatus skos:definition "Company Type (Legal Form of the entity)" .
rov:orgStatus skos:scopeNote "There is no agreed set of company types that crosses borders [rov:]. After examination,
EBG concluded there is no chance to \"standardize\" some shared super-types across jurisdictions. This said,
each jurisdiction will have a limited set of recognized company types and these should be expressed in a
consistent manner in a SKOS Concept Scheme [rov:] The types may form a hierarchy, but each company
can have maximum one value. Eg for Italy: Società Di Capitale > Società a responsabilità limitata [ebg:]" .

ebg:orgTypeText a rdf:Property, owl:DatatypeProperty .
ebg:orgTypeText schema:domainIncludes rov:RegisteredOrganization .
ebg:orgTypeText schema:rangeIncludes rdf:langString .
ebg:orgTypeText skos:scopeNote "Because of the difficulties of standardizing Type lookup, we include a free text field" .
ebg:orgTypeText skos:definition "Current entity status as reported by a national company register" .
ebg:orgTypeText skos:rules "include valid language tag (see [iana:] for list)" .
ebg:orgTypeText skos:example "Private Limited Company"@en .

ebg:license a rdf:Property, owl:DatatypeProperty .
ebg:license schema:domainIncludes ebg:DataItem .
ebg:license schema:rangeIncludes xsd:string .

ebg:certifiedEmailAddress a rdf:Property, owl:DatatypeProperty .
ebg:certifiedEmailAddress schema:domainIncludes rov:RegisteredOrganization .
ebg:certifiedEmailAddress schema:rangeIncludes xsd:string .

skos:altLabel a rdf:Property, owl:DatatypeProperty .
skos:altLabel schema:domainIncludes rov:RegisteredOrganization .
skos:altLabel schema:rangeIncludes rdfs:Literal .
skos:altLabel skos:scopeNote "Sometimes (e.g., when the legal name is very long) people refer to a
company using a different, informal version [ebg:]. Some jurisdictions recognize
concepts such as a trading name or alternative forms of a legal entity's name [rov:]" .
skos:altLabel skos:definition "Informal/popular name of the company (also called Trading As) [ebg:]" .
skos:altLabel skos:rules "Do not emit such name if it's equal to the legal name [ebg:]. 
Do not use this property to record translations of the primary legal name [rov:]. 
Provide a valid language tag if possible (see [iana:] for a list).
Don't allow leading, trailing and two consecutive spaces." .
skos:altLabel skos:example "OpenCorporates"@en .

ebg:wikipedia a rdf:Property, owl:DatatypeProperty .
ebg:wikipedia schema:domainIncludes rov:RegisteredOrganization .
ebg:wikipedia schema:rangeIncludes xsd:anyURI .

ebg:website a rdf:Property, owl:DatatypeProperty .
ebg:website schema:domainIncludes rov:RegisteredOrganization .
ebg:website schema:rangeIncludes xsd:anyURI .

ebg:propertyName a rdf:Property, owl:DatatypeProperty .
ebg:propertyName schema:domainIncludes ebg:DataItem .
ebg:propertyName schema:rangeIncludes xsd:string .

ebg:isPublic a rdf:Property, owl:DatatypeProperty .
ebg:isPublic schema:domainIncludes rov:RegisteredOrganization .
ebg:isPublic schema:rangeIncludes xsd:boolean .
ebg:isPublic skos:definition "Whether this is a public sector or publicly owned organisation" .

rov:orgActivity a rdf:Property, owl:DatatypeProperty .
rov:orgActivity schema:domainIncludes rov:RegisteredOrganization .
rov:orgActivity schema:rangeIncludes skos:Concept .
rov:orgActivity skos:definition "Economic activity of the organization." .
rov:orgActivity skos:scopeNote "Recorded using a controlled vocabulary, the preferred one is EC NACE 2. More detailed
national classifications are also useful, e.g. IT ATECO, UK SIC, BG NKID." .

rov:legalName a rdf:Property, owl:DatatypeProperty .
rov:legalName schema:domainIncludes rov:RegisteredOrganization .
rov:legalName schema:rangeIncludes rdfs:Literal .
rov:legalName skos:definition "The legal name of the business, i.e. official name of the company [ebg:]" .
rov:legalName skos:scopeNote "Provide a legal language tag (see [iana:] for a list), even if you need to guess
(e.g. if the company comes from the Italian register then the language is probably @it). 
Don't allow leading, trailing and two consecutive spaces." .
rov:legalName skos:example "Ontotext"@en .

locn:location a rdf:Property, owl:DatatypeProperty .
locn:location schema:domainIncludes rov:RegisteredOrganization .
locn:location schema:rangeIncludes dcterms:Location .

locn:address a rdf:Property, owl:DatatypeProperty .
locn:address schema:domainIncludes rov:RegisteredOrganization .
locn:address schema:rangeIncludes locn:Address .
